nějaký majetek
v Newfoundland v New Jersey.

57
00:06:50,598 --> 00:06:52,475
Asi půl akru půdy.

58
00:06:52,559 --> 00:06:54,018
Je tam i stará vlaková stanice.

59
00:06:54,060 --> 00:06:57,814
Mám tu pro vás odhad toho majetku.

60
00:06:59,899 --> 00:07:02,485
