- Nekecej?

96
00:11:18,992 --> 00:11:21,286
Já sem z Manhattanu, vole.

97
00:11:21,369 --> 00:11:22,912
Proč jsi tu? Práce?

98
00:11:22,912 --> 00:11:25,165
